http://www.tocaedit.com/donate

NOTE: Currently the hack only supports DirectX9, but Racer_S is
working on a solution.

I found that 16:9 users should set it to:
Width FOV: 0.75
Height FOV: 0.75

16:10 users:
Width FOV: 0.84
Height FOV: 0.84
